{'id': 30553014, 'body': "Thank you for the feedback, JKomo. We are currently working to add improvements to the PF App. We appreciate your support as we work to make our app better for you and all our members! 


Please note, you're more than welcome to check-in via your phone number, driver's license, or government issued state I.D.! The PF App is not required to workout in our clubs.
", 'modified': '2022-06-25T19:15:56Z'}

